docker-compose up
hit localhost:3000

Steps I took to create this sample project:

using fish shell:

frontend:
  - docker run -it --rm -v (pwd):/code node:alpine sh
  - yarn create react-app frontend

backend:
  - docker run -it --rm -v (pwd)/merv:/code elixir:alpine sh
  - mix archive.install hex phx_new
  - mix phx.new backend --no-ecto --no-gettext --no-html --no-live --no-assets

Also, study the docker-compose file.  It is VERY deliberately crafted.
